{"tid":449563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬧警阻上山野蠻惡港女被起底　極速刪fb潛水","createTime":"2017-10-27T09:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T06:09:47.000Z","uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"abc367ddb36f8a6301ac71bff746a352928f00ba","tid":449563,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"時事野黎，連仔唔好搬post thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大批觀霜市民昨因路面結霜被困大帽山，警方為防止意外昨起封山。不過有野蠻港女不滿警方「限制自由」，欲照衝上山，更不斷向警方「挑機」。片段一出街，即被網民公審及「人肉起底」。據悉，惡港女英文名為Jenny，曾在facebook曾就多項熱話新聞發言，包括近期銅鑼灣書店李波失蹤案等，但其fb在今早「極速」被關閉，似乎是擔心被「攻擊」，迅速「潛水」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160125/bkn-20160125103315212-0125_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160125%2Fbkn-20160125103315212-0125_00822_001.html&d=MX0V4rhuZCBpOgK%2F7GxHbBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=acc9514f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160125/bkn-20160125103315212-0125_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/153806_7f529b3c1f90c0c29d7c9ab90c85fba9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F153806_7f529b3c1f90c0c29d7c9ab90c85fba9.jpg&h=fe915d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警犬封路,仲有咩方法可以上到大帽山<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6224673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D6224673&d=MX0V4rhuZCBpOgK%2F7GxHbBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d1948ff1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6224673</a>"},{"pid":"73623b197e9f4641d2b8aaa105c9c737cb1da2fc","tid":449563,"uid":36035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf6d4e9c578897e4e8043cefb9e97fa88aa2b6e6","tid":449563,"uid":90863,"like":0